	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. in domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puto te accepisse literas, quas<note type="margin">a.R.: quasi!</note> misi per quęstorem aerarium a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20430" cert="high">Valentino Nusboum</persName> acceptas; si non accepisti, significa.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid censes futurum in conciliabulo Satanico <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName>?</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Episcopi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1028" cert="high">Trevirensis</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l307" cert="high">Maguntinensis</placeName> Selestadii fuere, sed honore solito sunt accepti, non episcopali; idem fecerunt et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l64" cert="high">Brisacenses</placeName> mei, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l922" cert="high">Friburgenses</placeName> autem honorifice campanis, candelis, vexillis, crucibus et reliquis; <foreign xml:lang="de">das gantz pfaffengeschwirm ist inen entgegen gezogen.</foreign></s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Episcopi crucibus dandis populo prodigi fuerunt; stultus populus indignus est ulla sana doctrina.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iam agunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName>; consultabunt omnia adversus Christum et verbum eius neque ob aliud convenerunt.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18">Augustę</placeName> quatuor episcopi consultarunt de concionatoribus eiiciendis; duo repugnarunt expectare volentes consilium papale, sed reliqui duo C [aesare] annuente cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanis</placeName> obtinuerunt, ut mox proscriberentur idque in terrorem reliquarum civitatum, quo vident <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesarem</persName> bene velle catholicis veteribus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid denique putas futurum cum principe optimo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1546" cert="high">Christophero Wirtembergensi</persName>?</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">annuet absque dubio ad omnia, quae Cęsariani praescripturi sunt ei tam in religione quam in aliis rebus exteris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Navigia quaedam contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> missa submersa sunt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l449">Silesia</placeName> est in armis, ne <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turca</placeName> irruat in confinia, idque ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l66" cert="high">Vratislaviensi</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">... aus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l66" cert="high">Breslau</placeName>.</note> habeo, qui hisce diebus apud nos fuit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernates</placeName> disceptant cum dominis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Theutonici</placeName> ordinis; nondum res ad finem deducta est.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vides, quomodo istud hominum genus cristas attollat, et nos ita insensati sumus, ut nihili curamus omnia, quę agunt, nihilque praemeditantes in futurum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo fit, quod nullę annotationes in 1. ep. Pauli ad Corinthios ad nos mittantur?</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale et rescribe; ocium enim nunc habes commodissimum.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto praeterea <persName ref="p8418" cert="high">Myconii</persName> nostri literas, qui lecto affixus est fere perpetuo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dux <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8098" cert="high">Georgius Wirtembergensis</persName> vocavit ad se Erbium; fortassis scripsit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1546" cert="high">Christophorus</persName> dux, ut ableget concionatores.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l491" cert="high">Argentinenses</placeName> habent <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18137">Marpachium</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l558" cert="high">Witenbergę</placeName>, qui consultet cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonibus</placeName>, hoc et <placeName ref="l558" cert="high">Wittenbergensibus</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l284" cert="high">Lipsiensibus</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Francofordiensi[bu]s</placeName>, quid velint respondere concilio suspecto <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi plura.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodorum</persName> salutabis meo nomine.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">10. septembris 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Ohne Unterschrift.]</note>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName> suo ad manus.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
